&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h6 id="big-data-in-biology-2023"&gt;Big Data in Biology (2023)&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I gave a &lt;strong&gt;flash talk&lt;/strong&gt; at the Basel Computational Biology Conference (BC2), held in Basel, Switzerland.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h6 id="short-guide-to-diving-into-scrna-seq-analysis-2020"&gt;Short Guide to Diving into scRNA-seq Analysis (2020)&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I recorded a &lt;strong&gt;video tutorial&lt;/strong&gt; for performing &lt;strong&gt;scRNA-seq analysis&lt;/strong&gt;, as part of the KeepScienceGoing Initiative during the COVID-19 pandemic, for others to learn how to analyze scRNA-seq data from scratch. More details at this &lt;a href="http://keepsciencegoing.org/ksg_tutorial_scrnaseq.html"&gt;(link)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SCQ5gedPDn8" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h6 id="hands-on-session-on-pca-for-dimensionality-reduction-2018"&gt;Hands-on Session on PCA for Dimensionality Reduction (2018)&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I gave a &lt;strong&gt;hands-on session&lt;/strong&gt; on using Principal Component Analysis (PCA) for dimensionality reduction of data in &lt;code&gt;R&lt;/code&gt;, at the EMBO-INDIA Symposia on Big Data in Biomedicine, New Delhi. The talk can be found on YouTube &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/bQbHP04_Oc4?t=25655"&gt;(link)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mixomania</title><link>https://www.arvindkiyer.com/blog/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.arvindkiyer.com/blog/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I write occasionally on &lt;a href="https://arvindkiyer.com/mixomania/"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mixomania&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, covering computational biology and related topics.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Contact</title><link>https://www.arvindkiyer.com/contact/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.arvindkiyer.com/contact/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Email is the best way to reach me.&lt;/p&gt;
